# Force LF line endings on every text file, regardless of the developer
# machine's core.autocrlf setting. Reproducible SHA-256 checksums for the
# embedded migration files require stable bytes across Windows and
# Linux/macOS checkouts; making the rule global keeps every text file
# consistent rather than fixing only the SQL instance of the problem.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Carve out binary files so Git never tries to normalize them.
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.pdf   binary
*.zip   binary
*.gz    binary
*.dll   binary
*.exe   binary
*.so    binary
*.dylib binary
